        "line_start": 7,
        "line_end": 13
      },
      "content": "1. Introduction\n1.1 Purpose\nThis document specifies the system-level requirements for the Autonomous Robot\nVacuum & Mop System (ARVMS).\nThe system shall autonomously clean indoor residential environments by: -\nVacuuming dry debris - Mopping hard floors - Navigating safely and efficiently -\nDocking automatically for charging",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G1",
      "gen_uid": "GU-05EDB3"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "1.1",
      "title": "Purpose",
      "level": 2,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 1,
        "line_start": 8,
        "line_end": 13
      },
      "content": "1.1 Purpose\nThis document specifies the system-level requirements for the Autonomous Robot\nVacuum & Mop System (ARVMS).\nThe system shall autonomously clean indoor residential environments by: -\nVacuuming dry debris - Mopping hard floors - Navigating safely and efficiently -\nDocking automatically for charging",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G1.1",
      "gen_uid": "GU-E6FA34"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "2",
      "title": "System Overview",
      "level": 1,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 1,
        "line_start": 14,
        "line_end": 24
      },
      "content": "2. System Overview\n2.1 Product Description\nARVMS is a mobile embedded system consisting of:\n• Mobile cleaning robot\n• Charging & maintenance dock\n• Mobile application\n• Optional cloud backend\n2.2 Operating Environment\nThe system shall operate in: - Indoor residential homes - Hard floors (tile,\nlaminate, wood) - Low/medium pile carpets - Ambient temperature: 5°C – 40°C\n- Humidity: 10% – 80%",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G2",
      "gen_uid": "GU-F16E05"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "2.1",
      "title": "Product Description",
      "level": 2,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 1,
        "line_start": 15,
        "line_end": 20
      },
      "content": "2.1 Product Description\nARVMS is a mobile embedded system consisting of:\n• Mobile cleaning robot\n• Charging & maintenance dock\n• Mobile application\n• Optional cloud backend",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G2.1",
      "gen_uid": "GU-07FE59"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "2.2",
      "title": "Operating Environment",
      "level": 2,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 1,
        "line_start": 21,
        "line_end": 24
      },
      "content": "2.2 Operating Environment\nThe system shall operate in: - Indoor residential homes - Hard floors (tile,\nlaminate, wood) - Low/medium pile carpets - Ambient temperature: 5°C – 40°C\n- Humidity: 10% – 80%",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G2.2",
      "gen_uid": "GU-76B82E"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "3",
      "title": "Functional Requirements",
      "level": 1,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 2,
        "line_start": 1,
        "line_end": 2
      },
      "content": "3. Functional Requirements\n3.1 Navigation",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G3",
      "gen_uid": "GU-DEA2DC"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "3.1",
      "title": "Navigation",
      "level": 2,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 2,
        "line_start": 2,
        "line_end": 12
      },
      "content": "3.1 Navigation\nSYS-FUNC-001\nThe system shall autonomously generate a 2D indoor map using SLAM.\nSYS-FUNC-002\nThe system shall localize itself with ±5 cm accuracy.\nSYS-FUNC-003\nThe system shall avoid static and dynamic obstacles in real-time.\nSYS-FUNC-004\nThe system shall detect cliffs or stairs and prevent falling.\nSYS-FUNC-005\nThe system shall support multi-room mapping and segmentation.",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G3.1",
      "gen_uid": "GU-5AC4F3"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "3.2",
      "title": "Vacuuming",
      "level": 2,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 2,
        "line_start": 13,
        "line_end": 19
      },
      "content": "3.2 Vacuuming\nSYS-FUNC-010\nThe system shall generate suction power >= 5000 Pa.\nSYS-FUNC-011\nThe system shall automatically adjust suction based on detected floor type.\nSYS-FUNC-012\nThe system shall detect carpet surfaces.",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G3.2",
      "gen_uid": "GU-EA7A22"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "3.3",
      "title": "Mopping",
      "level": 2,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 2,
        "line_start": 20,
        "line_end": 24
      },
      "content": "3.3 Mopping\nSYS-FUNC-020\nThe system shall provide electronically controlled water dispensing.\nSYS-FUNC-021\nThe system shall support adjustable water flow levels (Low/Medium/High).",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G3.3",
      "gen_uid": "GU-19EE92"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "3.4",
      "title": "Docking",
      "level": 2,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 3,
        "line_start": 5,
        "line_end": 12
      },
      "content": "3.4 Docking\nSYS-FUNC-030\nThe system shall automatically return to the charging dock when battery <\n20%.\nSYS-FUNC-031\nThe system shall resume cleaning after recharge.\nSYS-FUNC-032\nThe system shall support automatic charging.",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G3.4",
      "gen_uid": "GU-B5F185"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "3.5",
      "title": "User Interaction",
      "level": 2,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 3,
        "line_start": 13,
        "line_end": 19
      },
      "content": "3.5 User Interaction\nSYS-FUNC-040\nThe system shall support cleaning scheduling.\nSYS-FUNC-041\nThe system shall allow room-specific cleaning selection.\nSYS-FUNC-042\nThe system shall provide cleaning reports (area, duration, battery usage).",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G3.5",
      "gen_uid": "GU-38A9D5"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "4",
      "title": "Safety Requirements",
      "level": 1,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 3,
        "line_start": 20,
        "line_end": 21
      },
      "content": "4. Safety Requirements\n4.1 Mechanical Safety",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G4",
      "gen_uid": "GU-7696D5"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "4.1",
      "title": "Mechanical Safety",
      "level": 2,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 3,
        "line_start": 21,
        "line_end": 23
      },
      "content": "4.1 Mechanical Safety\nSYS-SAFE-001\nThe system shall stop all drive motors within 100 ms if lifted.",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G4.1",
      "gen_uid": "GU-39D125"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "4.2",
      "title": "Electrical Safety",
      "level": 2,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 4,
        "line_start": 5,
        "line_end": 9
      },
      "content": "4.2 Electrical Safety\nSYS-SAFE-010\nThe system shall prevent battery overcharge and deep discharge.\nSYS-SAFE-011\nThe system shall monitor motor temperature and prevent overheating.",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G4.2",
      "gen_uid": "GU-F50348"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "5",
      "title": "Performance Requirements",
      "level": 1,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 4,
        "line_start": 10,
        "line_end": 18
      },
      "content": "5. Performance Requirements\nSYS-PERF-001\nCleaning coverage efficiency shall be >= 95%.\nSYS-PERF-002\nMaximum noise level shall be <= 65 dB.\nSYS-PERF-003\nOperating time shall be >= 120 minutes.\nSYS-PERF-004\nCharging time shall be <= 4 hours.",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G5",
      "gen_uid": "GU-C88C33"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "6",
      "title": "Cybersecurity Requirements",
      "level": 1,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 4,
        "line_start": 19,
        "line_end": 21
      },
      "content": "6. Cybersecurity Requirements\nSYS-SEC-001\nAll external communications shall use TLS 1.2 or higher.",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G6",
      "gen_uid": "GU-096A25"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "7",
      "title": "Hardware Requirements",
      "level": 1,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 5,
        "line_start": 5,
        "line_end": 6
      },
      "content": "7. Hardware Requirements\n7.1 Sensors",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G7",
      "gen_uid": "GU-FA3403"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "7.1",
      "title": "Sensors",
      "level": 2,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 5,
        "line_start": 6,
        "line_end": 16
      },
      "content": "7.1 Sensors\nSYS-HW-001\nThe system shall include a LIDAR or vision-based navigation sensor.\nSYS-HW-002\nThe system shall include cliff detection sensors.\nSYS-HW-003\nThe system shall include wheel encoders.\nSYS-HW-004\nThe system shall include an IMU.\nSYS-HW-005\nThe system shall include a water level sensor.",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G7.1",
      "gen_uid": "GU-F54CC8"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "7.2",
      "title": "Actuators",
      "level": 2,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 5,
        "line_start": 17,
        "line_end": 23
      },
      "content": "7.2 Actuators\nSYS-HW-010\nThe system shall include two independent drive motors.\nSYS-HW-011\nThe system shall include a vacuum motor.\nSYS-HW-012\nThe system shall include a water pump.",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G7.2",
      "gen_uid": "GU-7E0AFD"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "8",
      "title": "Software Architecture Requirements",
      "level": 1,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 6,
        "line_start": 3,
        "line_end": 12
      },
      "content": "8. Software Architecture Requirements\nSYS-SW-001\nThe system shall implement a layered software architecture:\n• Application Layer\n• Middleware Layer\n• Hardware Abstraction Layer (HAL)\nSYS-SW-002\nThe system shall support modular firmware updates.\nSYS-SW-003\nThe system shall log diagnostic events with timestamps.",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G8",
      "gen_uid": "GU-25A38B"
    },
    {
      "spec_hierarchy_number": "9",
      "title": "System States",
      "level": 1,
      "spec_item_id": null,
      "loc": {
        "page": 6,
        "line_start": 13,
        "line_end": 18
      },
      "content": "9. System States\nThe system shall implement the following high-level states:\n• Idle\n• Mapping\n• Cleaning\n• Dockin",
      "gen_hierarchy_number": "G9",
      "gen_uid": "GU-717AFA"
    }
  ],
